did.head: Collection Summary

repository.corpname: Woodson Research Center, Rice University, Houston, Texas

did.abstract: This collection contains programs from football games.

bioghist.head: Biographical Sketch
bioghist.p: The programs trace the history of Rice University football from its inception until the present.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The programs include the names of the opposing institutions, dates of the games, pictures and background of the players

accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions
accessrestrict.p: This material is open for research
